[135.306037, "o", "\r\n\u001b[7m Manual page nmcli(1) line 86 (press h for help or q to quit)\u001b[27m\u001b[K\r\u001b[K \u001b[KESC\b\b\bESC\u001b[KO\bO\u001b[KB\bB\r\u001b[K           Output is pretty. This causes \u001b[1mnmcli \u001b[22mto produce easily readable outputs for\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[7m Manual page nmcli(1) line 87 (press h for help or q to quit)\u001b[27m\u001b[K\r\u001b[K \u001b[KESC\b\b\bESC\u001b[KO\bO\u001b[KB\bB\r\u001b[K           humans, i.e. values are aligned, headers are printed, etc.\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[7m Manual page nmcli(1) line 88 (press h for help or q to quit)\u001b[27m\u001b[K"]
