[157.51779899999997, "o", "\r\n"]
[157.51797799999997, "o", "\u001b[24;1H\r\u001b[K\u001b[7m Manual page nmcli(1) line 185 (press h for help or q to quit)\u001b[27m\u001b[K\r\u001b[K \u001b[KESC\b\b\bESC\u001b[KO\bO\u001b[KA\bA\r\u001b[K\u001b[H\u001bM               Reload the NetworkManager.conf configuration from disk. Note that this\u001b[m"]
